Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.47,0:00:50.32,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}脚下的街道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:52.89,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8\fad(0,521)}今天也一如往常
