Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.23,0:01:04.44,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}弄脏的衬衣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.44,0:01:06.42,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}沾染上了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:10.37,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}这自欺欺人的谎言…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.37,0:01:15.50,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8\fad(0,348)}我到底在保护什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.12,0:01:19.92,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}不畏失去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.92,0:01:23.63,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}即便长大成人 也心怀梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.63,0:01:25.63,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}因为我只希望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.63,0:01:28.15,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}自己能将这些
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.15,0:01:31.05,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8\fad(0,351)}视为骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.39,0:01:35.10,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}吐出来 舍弃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.10,0:01:36.98,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.98,0:01:38.73,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8\fad(0,347)}回忆起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.02,0:01:40.65,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.65,0:01:45.61,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8\fad(0,980)}希望明天我能这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.12,0:01:55.95,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8\fad(363,0)}在这个
