Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.98,0:22:31.70,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}误入这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:34.24,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\fad(0,349)}在此相遇的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.61,0:22:39.58,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\fad(0,1058)}最后一次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.38,0:22:53.84,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}东奔西走 苦苦找寻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.22,0:22:57.43,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\fad(0,349)}却毫无头绪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.01,0:23:03.48,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}狂风巨浪 风起云涌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.85,0:23:07.06,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\fad(0,355)}这残酷世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:10.94,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}你用最强的光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.94,0:23:13.11,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}照亮我模糊而单调的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.45,0:23:15.20,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}「谢谢你」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.53,0:23:17.57,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\fad(0,354)}我不是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.16,0:23:20.45,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}在昏沉的阴天下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.45,0:23:23.00,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}Cry Cry哭也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:27.13,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\fad(0,353)}抓住云间那一缕光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.75,0:23:30.05,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}这鲜红的证明流淌着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.05,0:23:32.42,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}疼痛难忍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.42,0:23:37.05,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}最后一次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.18,0:23:39.55,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\fad(525,0)}希望永不分离
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.55,0:23:42.06,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}希望笑容永驻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.06,0:23:46.19,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}希望生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.19,0:23:49.23,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}Ah 在这湛蓝的晴空下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.23,0:23:55.24,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\fad(0,518)}许下一个心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.24,0:23:57.03,ed,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.14,0:00:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他还活着？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.17,0:00:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事 冲田先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.69,0:00:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.38,0:00:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,虚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.36,0:00:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,吉田松阳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.71,0:00:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不 他现在说不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,以一种与这两者完全不同的状态存在着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.89,0:00:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他还活着
